definitions.definition: ( Greek mythology ) One of the three Fates ( Moirae ), daughter of Zeus and Themis ; the measurer of each thread of life . Her Roman equivalent is Decima .

main_definition: ( Greek mythology ) One of the three Fates ( Moirae ), daughter of Zeus and Themis ; the measurer of each thread of life . Her Roman equivalent is Decima .

definitions.definition: The venom of Lachesis muta , the bushmaster snake , used to treat various conditions.
